00.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Colin-Greenwood-and-Nick-Cave-1-696x435.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Colin-Greenwood-and-Nick-Cave-1-1392x870.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Colin-Greenwood-and-Nick-Cave-1-1068x668.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今天（9 月 4 日）宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radiohead">Radiohead 的</a>Colin Greenwood 将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave-and-the-bad-seeds">Nick Cave &amp; The Bad Seeds</a>一起参加他们即将举行的巡演。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong><strong>阅读更多：</strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-wild-god-review-3788381">尼克·凯夫和坏种子“狂野之神”评论：曾经的黑暗王子让光明进来</a></strong></li></ul><p>此前，乐队宣布马丁·凯西因病无法参加巡演。此前，格林伍德<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-announces-2024-european-solo-tour-buy-tickets-3614748">曾在凯夫最近的个人巡演中与凯夫一起现场演奏</a>，并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/warren-ellis">沃伦·埃利斯</a>一起参加过几次“大屠杀”巡演。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-the-making-of-wild-god-part-one-featuring-radioheads-colin-greenwood-3755873">格林伍德还为乐队的新专辑“Wild God”做出了贡献。</a></p><p>乐队在一份完整的公告中写道：“尼克·凯夫和坏种子乐队很遗憾地宣布，由于生病，马丁·凯西将不会参加即将举行的英国和欧洲巡演。</p><p> “科林·格林伍德将在这些节目中担任贝斯手。乐队向马丁表达了他们的爱和最美好的祝愿。”请在此处查看帖子全文： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_f0d3TIoJx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-g